      "text": "My father used to give him-- used to give him-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] equal in American money maybe a penny.",
